      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. I guess i'm curious about the actual drivers though. like when people talk about the shift from primitive to modern, they usually mention things like technology or organization. do you think there's a link between the type of culture or the ethnic background of a group and how quickly they move toward those complex modern structures? or is it just about resources?",
